  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9b4fd2de-ca8e-48f6-8d1a-bb2b4cf1064f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-07df8888-57fc-4b54-ab80-1c346784fb95\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-28a573b0-096e-490f-bc37-5d2875e04963\"><b>안녕하세요 사당동 한의원 </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e015d6e4-44eb-410b-b2ba-2d7ce5c10090\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-89cf7657-9a86-4178-bf0d-248d784cd36e\"><b> 입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-9b4fd2de-ca8e-48f6-8d1a-bb2b4cf1064f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8117c9fc-188a-45f2-a54c-776b0d52b2d2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"10\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_10.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-609bef3f-ff8a-4143-b73b-401b161f6aab\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-549403d8-1cec-40bd-881a-69a925cdb901\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27c18f26-19e1-4a42-b88f-a3229967f788\"><b>일상 통증, 혈자리로 풀어보세요 </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-65c953b4-e4dd-4547-85e9-a608f04a1df1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f21b2b5c-bc0e-4c35-b9ea-1c89dede1e20\">무릎이나 허리가 아프면 “나이 들어서 그래”라고 넘기기 쉽습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b30196f2-e00d-4bd7-8fc8-12f3e091e8c8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-56267f8c-d69a-4b58-ad3d-3d486b72c3c6\">하지만 이런 통증은 단순한 노화가 아닌, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e77b2a80-5c02-44cf-a1ca-a3681caf8b12\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-54e0687c-8204-4d37-8eed-1e75b8a40107\"><b>근육과 관절, 순환의 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b5aab872-bbb3-4d7d-8d42-a9cf84acd81f\">로부터 시작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-83603fa9-7261-4609-818e-1d8d2233cfb7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d5e2a1d7-736a-4825-a24b-813f30a0c1fe\">한의학에서는 이러한 통증을 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-01adf09d-36c6-4bae-8eb7-8e89e8c7726f\"><b>기혈(氣血)의 흐름 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e5632fe2-2cfe-41a3-a1d2-0f8bc89a551b\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-41a1fc02-90d9-4aa5-9550-771a220dae55\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a0510532-6b90-4e8a-80fd-e6b2483ade50\">또는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5ed4c766-8968-4bda-879c-34014819c5e3\"><b>경락(經絡)의 막힘</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0e09294e-bea9-440e-9fde-3555ecf27677\">으로 보고, 이를 풀어주는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e5a984c6-2610-4744-b23b-5799447ea584\"><b>혈자리 자극</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8a223439-749b-4ff9-a0aa-ca73c2f6c7cf\">으로 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3d7c4b96-25be-4a2a-824e-35a6df172499\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-61bc22db-00da-4604-9376-62d72b5060d8\">통증을 완화할 수 있다고 봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-609bef3f-ff8a-4143-b73b-401b161f6aab\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a06f215f-0a98-409f-8ee3-09fc4c5a699d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a06f215f-0a98-409f-8ee3-09fc4c5a699d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e9fe21915b3f78a1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1700\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e9fe21915b3f78a1.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e9fe21915b3f78a1.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a06f215f-0a98-409f-8ee3-09fc4c5a699d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5d97aa1c-fd0b-49c9-88f4-1fc90fb50fb4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fe25cd6a-3de3-4566-bee0-3bf31e95a385\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-add4632a-b258-44a4-bc41-6d109cdbadf8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5fc9d770-30ba-4497-a08d-954f5e8d2ec9\"><b>📍 무릎관절 통증에 좋은 혈자리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c9700563-1493-43a9-9113-0053cca94f25\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d05a34ce-f546-472a-a712-896291835487\"><b>1. 족삼리(足三里)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0f274a02-4010-41df-8977-f6edae62f25a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a3c12a39-627f-4de4-ac4e-030ba441dbcb\">위치: 무릎 아래 약 4가락(약 3~4cm) 정도 떨어진 정강이 바깥쪽</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d67034a5-4349-4e18-b7d8-e542e0c0a907\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d3acbfc1-f580-4c83-9511-d66402d4611e\"><b>효과: </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f02e8dbc-9ea1-462f-b23d-72e167683953\">기혈 순환을 원활히 해 무릎 주변의 피로와 통증을 줄여줍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-916fedc6-a7cb-4f29-8090-0d2257829022\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-00af34aa-9ba3-4254-9690-3b8dd87b6891\">일반적으로 무릎이 무겁고 시큰할 때 많이 쓰이는 대표 혈자리입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ba784340-4a37-4080-aa37-afa843533545\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-fbf3d8e3-3000-4e68-b7d0-b596fe88bb4d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3a7c53a4-f73f-444c-a22d-f36bc524e9ee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-acf01550-c891-41c1-b96c-180ae563f5b0\"><b>2. 양릉천(陽陵泉)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fc9f1fca-6016-49ca-970e-4d95a92eb8d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a360bb4e-dc1e-42c9-9aaf-d5eb329443d8\">위치: 종아리 바깥쪽, 무릎 바로 아래의 오목한 부분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2e942164-7fc7-42db-9131-423bf248b5c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0f7be901-e841-4410-84d9-9cd01f8421db\">효과: 다리의 근육 경직, 관절통에 효과적이며, 특히 움직일 때 무릎이 뻣뻣한 경우에 유용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-fe25cd6a-3de3-4566-bee0-3bf31e95a385\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8df8e80-dc43-4c59-a089-293c86241ddc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a8df8e80-dc43-4c59-a089-293c86241ddc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0de8f3da15fd2146.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0de8f3da15fd2146.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0de8f3da15fd2146.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-a8df8e80-dc43-4c59-a089-293c86241ddc\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-6728b485-ad64-48a6-9680-08dd40641f9e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7df8520a-dd5a-41ea-80ab-6e0871f96963\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54dec508-cd21-4856-bb38-401aee2c30e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-50ac6750-0218-4959-8334-7a58e2fc2a69\"><b>📍 허리 통증에 좋은 혈자리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-90f2b4bb-40ae-43e4-9572-bed5e93baeee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-44d4099c-e848-4606-8eb9-e52550980cf3\"><b>3. 위중(委中)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-35a200c1-9658-427e-950e-8cb6388000ec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-03e13ce9-add1-434d-8603-083bb472272c\">위치: 무릎 뒤쪽 중앙, 오금이라고 불리는 부분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3817bb9c-11f2-4d27-a293-83b1198f5875\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6d485c61-c5da-4d2f-9735-d6bdc655c8f0\">효과: ‘허리의 혈’이라 불릴 정도로, </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-91a3bf76-513a-4451-bdd7-ec36089e7c01\"><b>요통에 탁월한 효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-590d9847-17b7-4834-9689-0cd679f87f86\">가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-edaa4fd5-d655-4f16-b1bc-15960fbfb487\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c841346c-247f-46a4-81de-2282b3ddad48\">허리 근육이 뻣뻣하거나 앉았다 일어날 때 아플 경우에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0dfe1d39-66c6-4862-84ad-46c7e672e275\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-13e674db-b08c-4f81-96e6-8b60fc0d7c5e\">특히 자주 사용합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-34b36510-9066-4daf-8b7d-ee489883f9d0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-02332a07-0e09-4607-b307-3f5222298dfc\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dadf4003-9f12-419b-be77-d3a9814f0d87\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-032f110b-aab6-4792-95ba-f93025caeb57\"><b>4. 신수(腎兪)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5e09c450-a474-4c13-ae98-320c2a85635f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b99c0cfd-ad63-411c-b844-417d4db407db\">위치: 허리뼈에서 손가락 두 마디 옆, 양쪽 척추 옆 근육 부위</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1153934-3e81-40b7-9abb-8938c2b2d5bd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3c850a3b-a4c7-40d3-86d9-46dd6adfed60\">효과: 신장의 기운을 보강하여 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9c761032-3e75-45bf-a259-64420870303e\"><b>허리 힘 부족, 만성 요통, 하체 냉증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-79611545-faaa-4301-9c7e-75f02abffa2f\"> 등에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f5b3d12-124f-4581-927a-131e21197d11\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-189e2f4f-51b5-4cbd-9eaa-7d04627c1ce4\">효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fbbbe986-3776-4572-bc48-9e6721fc3e5b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-cfe230e5-0dc1-4ee6-89e9-e3f5a7411218\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dc25842c-ec73-44d3-afee-c7fb84f259c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b0c2ea14-cc40-495d-8dad-b8a5183c064b\"><b>5. 요양관(腰陽關)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-t